{"product_id":"raglan-cropped-tee-coffee","title":"RAGLAN CROPPED TEE - COFFEE","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium French Terry Cotton. Cropped Silhouette with Raglan Full Sleeves. Minimal Design. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cropped 240 GSM full-sleeve T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted for a clean, super-decent everyday look. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to maintain the fabric’s integrity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM French terry fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Cropped length with full raglan sleeves for a relaxed, modern fit. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton for all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish ensures durability and a smooth hand feel.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47500127174810,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47500127207578,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47500127240346,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(